405}, {\"ngram\": \"a respectable 18th place\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10km event\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he's issued a brutally honest verdict on how it went and said he's already 'retiring' from this particular competition.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brutally honest verdict\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"this particular competition\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked how he felt after his first open water swim, Wiffen joked: 'And last, and last.'\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first open water swim\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's one of the worst things I have ever done,' he told RTE Sport.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999989440767, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RTE Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst things\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m never doing it again\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dDaniel Wiffen absolutely delighted he finished the 10km marathon swim in the Seine and announces his retirement from \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098open water\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 \\u00e2\\u0098\\u0098\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fpic.twitter.com/QIap4fIQ5W 'But yeah, I am happy I did it.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999983745056, \"rank\": 1.6096102882149265e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"again\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dDaniel Wiffen\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10km marathon swim\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098open\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0098\\u0098\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fpic.twitter.com/QIap4fIQ5W\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I can say that I can range from 10k.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10k\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I actually placed higher than I did in Tokyo in the pools so I am pretty proud of myself.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999958968728656, \"rank\": 3.223078821607345e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pools\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But, you know, when you get to halfway, all I was thinking was \\\"I am already an Olympic champion and I am swimming this and I am coming 18th\\u2026\\\" 'I was like, \\\"oh I will just finish it now, but then I am never doing it again\\\".'\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen was also taken aback by the brutal nature of the open water swim and says he much prefers the less chaotic pool events after taking a few hits to the face.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the brutal nature\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"the open water swim\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"the less chaotic pool events\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"a few hits\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'All the coaches are laughing because I was swimming out by myself because I wasn't arsed going behind somebody,' he said.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the coaches\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'All I was thinking was \\\"yeah, I can not be arsed to get kicked in the face\\\".\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I got a couple of elbows in the eye and I got punched in the face at one point.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"elbows\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"the eye\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This sport is not for me I do not think.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This sport\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely want my own lane next time.'\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own lane\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen, who finished the race in just under two hours, said he even considered 'pulling out' beforehand but 'wanted to do it because my friends are'.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"just under two hours\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"beforehand\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not actually see any of them apart from my training partner Toby [Robinson] from GB,' he joked.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9810325942751127, \"rank\": 0.019301524158368392, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my training partner\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My goal coming into this was to finish and I am very pleased with myself and happy to say I did not come last, so that's the main thing.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My goal\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"the main thing\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am so happy I have completed it and I am retiring from open water.'\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"open water\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on his incredible time at the Olympics, he added: 'I could not ask for anything more.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his incredible time\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Becoming an Olympic champion ages ago now it seems, about a week-and-a-half ago, and then a bronze medal as well.\", \"from\": 24